extends layout

block content
  div.container.backdrop
    h1.text-center Image Search Abstraction Layer
    h2 User stories:
    ol
     li I can get the image URLs, alt text and page urls for a set of images relating to a given search string.
     li I can paginate through the responses by adding a ?offset=2 parameter to the URL.
     li I can get a list of the most recently submitted search strings.
     
    h2 Example usage:
    p.
      #{url}  -  <strong>Show this page</strong> <br />
      #{url}latest - <strong>Show most recently submitted search stringse</strong> <br />
      #{url}search/rain - <strong>Show image data relating to "rain"</strong> <br />
      #{url}search/rain?offset=10 - <strong>Show image data relating to "rain" startng at offset 10</strong>

